summary: An armor mod from TERA Online, converted to CBBE SE with physics
descriptionHtml:
[color=#1e84cc][size=6]CBBE SE - Tera Rogue Armor [/size][/color][size=3]
[/size][i][size=4]An armor mod [color=#f1f1f1]featuring the rogue [/color][/size][size=4]outfit from Tera for Skyrim SE![/size]

[/i]
[color=#1e84cc][size=5]﻿- WHAT'S INCLUDED -[/size][/color]
[b][/b][center] Tera Rogue Outfit
Tera Rogue Outfit Skirt
Tera Rogue Glove 
Tera Rogue Boots
Tera Rogue Boots 2[/center]
[color=#1e84cc][size=5]- REQUIREMENTS - [/size][/color][size=3][color=#1e84cc] [/color]
[/size]
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/198]CBBE SE Body
﻿[/url][color=#f1f1f1]﻿[/color][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/1988]HDT physics compatible skeleton
[/url][color=#f1f1f1]﻿[/color][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/201]The latest Bodyslide[/url][color=#f1f1f1]﻿﻿ (Optional)[/color]
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/13207]CBP Physics[/url][color=#f1f1f1]﻿﻿ or [/color][url=http://www.9damao.com/thread-61878-1-1.html]HDT SMP[/url][color=#f1f1f1]﻿ (For Boobs and Butt Jiggle) [/color]
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/18045?]RaceMenu High Heels[/url][color=#f1f1f1]﻿ for the Heels effect[/color]

[color=#1e84cc][size=5]- INSTALLATION -[/size][/color][size=3][color=#1e84cc] [/color]
[/size]
[color=#f1f1f1]1. Download and install this mod (automatically, using NMM or MO2, or Vortex, or if manually then extract the file into SkyrimSE's Data folder).[/color]
[color=#f1f1f1]2. Obtain in-game via crafting at any tanner rack or by using [/color][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/17563]AdditemMenu SE[/url][color=#f1f1f1]﻿[/color]
[color=#f1f1f1]3. The default body is CBBE Curvy. If you wish to customize your shape then read on.[/color]
[color=#f1f1f1]4. Download and install the Bodyslide and Outfit Studio﻿ utility.[/color]
[color=#f1f1f1]5. Open the BodySlide utility. Search for "CBBE SE - Tera Rogue Outfit"[/color]
[color=#f1f1f1]6. Tweak the sliders to your liking, or use a preset that you have already created.[/color]
[color=#1e84cc][size=5]- Credits -[/size][/color][size=3][color=#1e84cc] [/color]
[/size]
[size=3]Shocky,[/size][color=#f1f1f1] [/color][size=3]En Masse Entertainment, and [/size]Bluehole Studios[color=#f1f1f1] for the permission to share this with you guys![/color]
[i][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/users/84177]Jeir[/url]﻿ & [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/users/4291759]Ousnius[/url]﻿ [size=2]for the CBBE SE female body replacer and the Bodyslide and Outfit Studio utility.[/size][/i]
author: Andreis
